data.description: The Rainbow Academy was established in 2003 in response to requests from divers and non-divers alike who were looking for a professional and focused approach to diver education.Here we teach you to become a professional dive educator as a Divemaster or Instructor. Programs start every month and run for 3-6 months.The Academy is managed by PADI Master Instructor Matthew Shaw and supported by an international team of experienced Instructor-Trainers, including the only 2 Course Directors in Vietnam.
